ABOUT
-----

AndroidSensors is a small project to test the Android SDK.

FEATURES
--------

AndroidSensors allows the selection of different sensors found
in Android phones like accelerometers.

It reads the sensor values (x, y, and z direction)
and translates them into an RGB color value which
is then displayed on the screen.

REQUIREMENTS
------------

Android SDK - API version 10

LICENSE
-------

